{"tid":1120375,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【馮仁昭四圍超】 過檔ViuTV夥ERROR拍飲食節目 黃淑儀宜蘭遇地震：好驚","createTime":"2019-04-22T15:16:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-22T15:19:29.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8874790eb0f44ce8673b42f1c09dd843c2f83e0f","tid":1120375,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T15:16:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20190422/20661238\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190422%2F20661238&d=%2BBr8udGLiiUmorY0Hhmb0hFNIXSBonesC3SPsSCGYVE%3D&h=045ec43f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190422%2F20661238&h=d70ae81b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20190422/20661238</a><br />\n<br />\n【馮仁昭四圍超】<br />\n過檔ViuTV夥ERROR拍飲食節目<br />\n黃淑儀宜蘭遇地震：好驚<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190422/large/22ec3p1a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190422%2Flarge%2F22ec3p1a.jpg&h=a2786a87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃淑儀喺宜蘭拍攝期間遇地震，感到驚同埋擔心。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n黃淑儀（GiGi姐）服務無綫50年，今年1月約滿離巢後，原來已過檔ViuTV。早前GiGi姐偕ERROR成員梁業（肥仔）同吳保錡，到台灣拍全新烹飪綜藝節目，不過台灣花蓮日前發生6.1級地震，前日凌晨宜蘭近海再發生3.2級地震，目前眾人正喺宜蘭拍嘢，噚日更兵分兩路，肥仔同保錡到宜蘭海邊拍攝時再遇輕微餘震。ViuTV公關部回覆指唔會因地震取消外景，但絕對會喺安全情況下工作，攝製隊目前正離開宜蘭到台南取景。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190422/large/22ec3p2a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190422%2Flarge%2F22ec3p2a.jpg&h=9bf55642&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃淑儀帶隊到台灣農場參觀。<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190422/large/22ec3p3a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190422%2Flarge%2F22ec3p3a.jpg&h=8c8e4201&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n過檔ViuTV後嘅黃淑儀（左），再主持烹飪節目。<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190422/large/22ec3p20a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190422%2Flarge%2F22ec3p20a.jpg&h=d2f21443&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n肥仔（左）同保錡到宜蘭拍攝時，亦遇上地震。<br />\n<br />\n「我啲細路喺台北」<br />\n<br />\n記者噚日聯絡GiGi姐、肥仔及保錡，三人拍一段短片回應。保錡問有否遇過地震？肥仔話：「啱啱咪地震囉，頭先搖嚟搖去好似喺架船度，搖到好犀利咪就係囉。」GiGi姐話：「你哋都感覺到有地震呀？因為我哋睇到新聞話宜蘭呢邊又有、花蓮又有、台北又有，所以我都好驚，因為我啲細路喺台北度假，你哋又去咗海邊，我幾驚呀！」<br />\n<br />\nGiGi姐續稱：「會唔會影響到你哋呢？我真係好擔心，但因為我哋呢邊坐喺車行緊公路，所以冇咁大嘅感覺。」佢又問二人當時情況，肥仔話：「當時震咗3、4秒，唔係震好耐，所以嗰一刻我哋唔知地震，震完之後導演話『啱啱地震呀！』先知。」<br />\n<br />\n撰文：馮仁昭  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n藍潔瑛墓碑遭熏黑<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n【馮仁昭四圍超】楊丞琳攻日 粉絲學中文"},{"pid":"a08dcced6f79de993e2608dd570b3d68cf8399fc","tid":1120375,"uid":114537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T15:19:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}